<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM2.5.6">
<l>cērntār tīviṉaikaṭ karunañcait tiṇmatiyai</l>
<l>tīrntār tammaṉattup piriyā tavaruyiraic</l>
<l>cōrntē pōkalkoṭā cuṭarai yarakkiyaimūk</l>
<l>kīrntāyai yaṭiyē ṉaṭaintēṉ mutaṉmuṉṉamē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O bane to the evil karma of those who join [you], firm mind,</l>
<l>their life that does not separate from the minds of those who quit,</l>
<l>effulgence that trickles [and] does not give going(?), you who sawed off</l>
<l>the nose of the rakṣasi, I [your] servant have finally reached you as [my] base.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
